XeraHub  
Open-source, fully customizable ESP Hub for Rooms & Doors.

XeraHub is designed to make gameplay smoother, clearer and easier by providing
advanced ESP features, bright-mode tools, per-entity customization and clean UI controls.
This project is fully open-source under the MIT License.

For transparency:  
XeraHub sends a minimal non-harmful execution log (UserName, UserId, Executor)  
to the developer for usage analytics only.  
No harmful actions are performed.  
No sensitive or private data is collected.

Source code is fully available for review.
